
---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Zoom 49 – Weeks">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-8">Weeks Hub</h1>
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-1" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 1 – The Inheritance of Chaos
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        The recursive system destabilizes and meaning begins to fracture.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-2" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 2 – The Recursive Signal
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        The team begins to suspect intention behind the chaos.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-3" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 3 – The Stress Test
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        The system is no longer mysterious. It is alive. And alive systems are defined not by smoothness but by adaptive resilience.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-4" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 4 – The Fracture Point
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        The system's resilience is tested to its limits, revealing critical vulnerabilities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-5" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 5 – Phantom Protocols
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        Where recursion meets AI mischief, and the team begins negotiating influence with the system itself.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-6" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 6 – The Predictive Play
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        Where awareness transforms into strategy, and the Tristero reveals its patterns.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-7" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 7 – The Tristero Revealed
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        Where patterns coalesce, and the system becomes a mirror of both participants and observers.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-signal transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        <a href="/weeks/week-12" class="hover:text-signal">
          Week 12 – The Meta-Loop
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">
        The system's influence becomes recursive, and the team must adapt to a new level of complexity.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 text-neutral-400">
      Week 13 – Signal Pending
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
